NestSettings.AwayOvenWarning.Name: Off While Away
NestSettings.AwayOvenWarning.Description: Receive a notification asking if youd like to turn your oven off if Nest detects you're away while your oven is running.   Please note that it may take up to two hours for Nest to send the away signal.
